javax.accessibility.Accessible, java.awt.event.ActionListener, java.util.EventListener, java.awt.image.ImageObserver, java.awt.ItemSelectable, javax.swing.event.ListDataListener, java.awt.MenuContainer, java.io.Serializable
public class FijiInputComboBox
extends javax.swing.JComboBox

An input box to allow command-line input into FIJI interpreter. Each line is parsed, echoed in the text window and executed with results to the text window. It's also saved in the dropdown so that if the user makes a selection it's as good as typing it in.
